Leave him.

00:08:45.380 --> 00:08:46.140
Let's go.

00:08:59.740 --> 00:09:00.380
Thanks.

00:09:01.940 --> 00:09:02.660
Zhou Xiao.

00:09:07.380 --> 00:09:08.060
Hey, it's you.

00:09:09.060 --> 00:09:09.820
Are you okay?

00:09:11.020 --> 00:09:11.820
Yes.

00:09:13.020 --> 00:09:14.620
