00:09:29.300 --> 00:09:30.780
But it's shameful to cry out here.

00:09:34.220 --> 00:09:34.780
Come on.

00:10:11.980 --> 00:10:14.060
So Zhao Fanzhou really broke up with you?

00:10:14.620 --> 00:10:15.500
Why?

