00:10:31.060 --> 00:10:32.780
Kneel down and beg him?

00:10:33.820 --> 00:10:36.140
I'll break your legs if you dare to do that.

00:10:39.700 --> 00:10:42.060
No, I'll break his legs.

00:10:44.060 --> 00:10:44.980
Sit down. Sit down.

00:11:00.380 --> 00:11:02.380
