Look.

00:12:48.340 --> 00:12:49.420
Bubble fireworks.

00:12:50.620 --> 00:12:51.460
Are you touched?

00:12:52.100 --> 00:12:52.700
Yeah.

00:12:53.060 --> 00:12:55.700
Look at the glorious fireworks
I set off for you.

00:12:59.340 --> 00:13:06.060
♪but there is only sorrow in my world.♪

00:13:09.060 --> 00:13:17.020
♪I don't want to live in sorrow...♪

00:13:17.020 --> 00:13:18.380
You didn't tell me

00:13:18.380 --> 00:13:20.460
because you didn't want me to be scared?

00:13:21.180 --> 00:13:21.900
Hmm.

00:13:23.020 --> 00:13:23.980
How about you?

00:13:23.980 --> 00:13:24.980
Are you scared?

00:13:25.420 --> 00:13:26.140
Hmm.

00:13:26.580 --> 00:13:28.940
Don't be afraid. I'm with you.

00:13:29.180 --> 00:13:30.420
Don't look down upon me.

00:13:30.820 --> 00:13:33.180
When I was a kid,
I dared to stir up a hornets' nest.

00:13:35.420 --> 00:13:36.860
But Zhou Xiao,

00:13:37.260 --> 00:13:39.860
this matter is more serious than that.

00:13:40.620 --> 00:13:42.420
How can I be so selfish?

