So for this semester,

00:14:17.700 --> 00:14:19.140
I listed works

00:14:19.140 --> 00:14:21.340
of western literature that you must read.

00:14:21.580 --> 00:14:22.780
Write them down.

00:14:23.540 --> 00:14:24.380
I hope

00:14:25.060 --> 00:14:26.060
at the end of this semester,

00:14:26.420 --> 00:14:27.740
every one of you will have

00:14:28.100 --> 00:14:29.620
read at least half of them.

00:14:32.140 --> 00:14:33.820
