Come in.

00:16:33.340 --> 00:16:34.540
Hello, what can I do for you?

00:16:34.860 --> 00:16:36.260
Hello, I'm from the Detective Club.

00:16:36.500 --> 00:16:37.620
I came for an election form.

00:16:37.620 --> 00:16:38.500
Wait a moment.

00:16:38.500 --> 00:16:39.220
Okay.

00:16:39.780 --> 00:16:42.940
Do you know Zhao Fanzhou
applied for withdrawal

00:16:42.940 --> 00:16:43.820
from the Student Union?

00:16:44.300 --> 00:16:45.540
Yes.

00:16:45.540 --> 00:16:47.220
He's really a strange man.

00:16:47.220 --> 00:16:48.660
There's going to be an election already

00:16:49.180 --> 00:16:51.260
and he wants to withdraw now.

00:16:51.860 --> 00:16:54.340
Chen Yu has gone back to his own school.

00:16:54.420 --> 00:16:55.660
Now I have to do

00:16:55.660 --> 00:16:57.220
all of the work.

00:16:57.580 --> 00:16:58.820
It's wearing me out.

00:17:02.540 --> 00:17:03.300
Hey.

00:17:04.540 --> 00:17:05.260
Thanks.

00:17:41.300 --> 00:17:42.380
Ms. Huang.

00:17:43.660 --> 00:17:44.820
Zhou Xiao.

00:17:44.820 --> 00:17:45.900
You came at a good moment.

00:17:46.140 --> 00:17:48.700
Help me post a want ad of the library

00:17:48.740 --> 00:17:50.100
on the campus forum.

