I tried to release it

00:17:51.940 --> 00:17:53.420
but it kept saying that I failed.

00:17:53.660 --> 00:17:54.860
A want ad?

00:17:54.860 --> 00:17:56.340
Are we short-handed at the moment?

00:17:56.500 --> 00:17:59.300
Yes. The juniors need to do internships

00:17:59.620 --> 00:18:00.900
instead of part-time jobs.

00:18:01.020 --> 00:18:03.300
Hasn't your Zhao Fanzhou quit his, too?

00:18:04.260 --> 00:18:05.620
Yes, he has.

00:18:06.060 --> 00:18:07.020
I'll send it to your email.

00:18:07.020 --> 00:18:08.580
Help me upload it.

00:18:08.620 --> 00:18:09.220
Okay.

00:18:11.340 --> 00:18:13.260
Zhou Xiao, I've sent it to your email.

00:18:13.260 --> 00:18:13.980
Have a look at it.

00:18:14.500 --> 00:18:14.980
Okay.

