Dear president,

00:18:41.700 --> 00:18:45.060
I'm Zhao Fanzhou from the Department
of Forensic Medicine.

00:18:45.780 --> 00:18:47.900
It was a great honor
to join the Detective Club.

00:18:48.980 --> 00:18:50.860
For some personal reasons,

00:18:50.900 --> 00:18:53.060
I can't take part in activities
of the club anymore.

00:18:53.900 --> 00:18:55.740
Now I'm applying for withdrawal from it.

00:18:56.900 --> 00:18:59.020
I hope the Detective Club
will be better and better.

00:18:59.460 --> 00:19:00.460
Please approve of my application.

00:19:01.260 --> 00:19:03.300
Applicant: Zhao Fanzhou.

00:19:06.740 --> 00:19:08.900
Zhou Xiao, did you receive the email?

00:19:11.260 --> 00:19:12.300
Yes.

00:19:18.700 --> 00:19:21.060
(Your application has been approved.)

00:19:24.540 --> 00:19:26.700
(Hello, Zhao Fanzhou)

00:19:31.540 --> 00:19:35.620
(Your application has been approved.)

00:20:08.620 --> 00:20:09.620
Zhou,

00:20:09.940 --> 00:20:10.940
have some fruit.

00:20:11.420 --> 00:20:12.860
Lu insisted on buying it for me.

00:20:12.860 --> 00:20:13.660
She said

00:20:13.660 --> 00:20:15.180
I had to eat fruit in all kinds

00:20:15.340 --> 00:20:16.580
of colors every day

00:20:16.940 --> 00:20:18.060
and only then would my skin

00:20:18.060 --> 00:20:19.060
be rosy

00:20:19.060 --> 00:20:19.900
and different.

00:20:22.140 --> 00:20:22.820
No, thanks.

00:20:23.620 --> 00:20:25.860
I've washed it. Eat some.

00:20:25.940 --> 00:20:26.820
This is a gift

00:20:26.820 --> 00:20:27.820
my girlfriend prepared for me.

00:20:28.220 --> 00:20:30.380
I'm so generous
and want to share it with you.

00:20:30.620 --> 00:20:31.740
Unlike me,

00:20:32.380 --> 00:20:34.580
you never shared what Zhou Xiao gave you.

00:20:40.820 --> 00:20:41.820
Sorry, Zhou.

00:20:42.260 --> 00:20:42.740
I...

00:20:43.300 --> 00:20:45.380
I forgot that you had broken up.

00:20:46.100 --> 00:20:47.180
Don't get cross.

00:20:48.980 --> 00:20:51.020
Why don't you eat some fruit and cool down?

00:20:55.580 --> 00:20:56.820
Are you leaving me again?

00:20:59.140 --> 00:21:00.620
What I mean is

00:21:02.020 --> 00:21:03.100
that I, well,

00:21:03.220 --> 00:21:05.060
I won a national championship.

00:21:05.100 --> 00:21:06.300
I want to share

00:21:06.300 --> 00:21:07.060
my joy with you.

00:21:07.620 --> 00:21:09.060
Share it with your Lu.

00:21:09.620 --> 00:21:11.660
Of course I've shared it with her.

00:21:11.980 --> 00:21:13.700
Aren't we good friends?

00:21:13.740 --> 00:21:15.420
I also need to share it with you.

00:21:16.220 --> 00:21:17.860
You know what?

00:21:18.780 --> 00:21:19.660
I'll get my prize today.

00:21:20.180 --> 00:21:21.420
Go after we have a celebration dinner.

00:21:23.620 --> 00:21:24.380
I'm not free for that.

00:21:25.700 --> 00:21:25.940
Hey.

00:21:27.060 --> 00:21:28.420
How could you reply like that?

00:21:28.980 --> 00:21:29.820
Aren't you being a spoilsport?

00:21:38.660 --> 00:21:39.660
Zhou,

00:21:40.620 --> 00:21:42.940
do you know how big my prize is?

00:21:44.740 --> 00:21:45.940
A hundred and fifty thousand.

00:22:03.660 --> 00:22:04.420
You are here.

00:22:10.620 --> 00:22:12.140
Just say what's up.

00:22:41.860 --> 00:22:43.260
Just now I hit you

00:22:43.260 --> 00:22:44.260
as Zhou Xiao's good friend.

00:22:45.340 --> 00:22:46.300
You could break up with her

00:22:46.580 --> 00:22:47.820
but you didn't even have a proper reason.

00:22:48.060 --> 00:22:49.140
Isn't that too awful?

00:22:56.220 --> 00:22:56.740
Now

00:22:57.260 --> 00:22:59.100
I'll speak to you as someone
who likes Zhou Xiao.

00:23:00.540 --> 00:23:01.180
Thanks.

00:23:02.580 --> 00:23:03.980
After all, you gave me a chance

00:23:04.620 --> 00:23:05.420
to be with Zhou Xiao.

00:23:06.940 --> 00:23:08.340
Don't let her see you again.

00:23:10.180 --> 00:23:10.780
Okay.

00:23:12.620 --> 00:23:13.940
Don't you have other things to say?

00:23:14.140 --> 00:23:16.220
Is she so dispensable to you?

00:23:20.500 --> 00:23:21.860
Take good care of her.

00:23:29.140 --> 00:23:30.380
I will take good care of her

00:23:31.100 --> 00:23:32.300
and even better than you.

00:23:34.340 --> 00:23:35.460
We've known each other for such a long time.

00:23:36.180 --> 00:23:37.380
I know Zhou Xiao the best.

00:23:38.860 --> 00:23:39.820
Good.

00:23:42.780 --> 00:23:44.820
She often forgets to eat
when she's busy writing.

00:23:48.540 --> 00:23:49.660
Even if you put

00:23:50.420 --> 00:23:51.540
the food in front of her,

00:23:52.980 --> 00:23:53.980
she still won't eat it.

00:23:56.060 --> 00:23:57.620
If you feed her,

00:23:59.580 --> 00:24:00.860
she'll eat it without having a look at it.

00:24:04.780 --> 00:24:06.780
She won't watch out
for cars when crossing the road.

00:24:08.460 --> 00:24:09.300
Watch out!

00:24:11.620 --> 00:24:13.340
You have to get mad at her.

00:24:13.460 --> 00:24:14.860
Only then will she take it seriously.

00:24:15.500 --> 00:24:17.420
Surprised? Shocked? Moved?

00:24:17.660 --> 00:24:19.180
Don't you watch out for cars
while crossing the street?

