00:44:13.540 --> 00:44:15.180
Aren't you too kind-hearted?

00:44:15.300 --> 00:44:16.100
If you want to do a good deed,

00:44:16.100 --> 00:44:17.420
donate lunch on the Internet.

00:44:18.020 --> 00:44:19.300
She asked you to go there

00:44:19.300 --> 00:44:20.140
as an elder.

00:44:20.300 --> 00:44:21.900
She was taking the high road.

00:44:22.100 --> 00:44:22.820
Can you not talk nonsense

00:44:22.820 --> 00:44:24.260
when you know nothing?

00:44:24.620 --> 00:44:25.860
What shall I know?

00:44:26.980 --> 00:44:28.540
You just don't wanna break up with him.

00:44:28.540 --> 00:44:29.940
You still like him.

00:44:30.380 --> 00:44:31.780
Cut the bullshit.

00:44:31.940 --> 00:44:33.740
Mrs. Zhao is in the Department of Psychiatry.

00:44:39.180 --> 00:44:41.140
What on earth are you following me for?

00:44:41.140 --> 00:44:42.460
You said Zhao Fanzhou's mom

00:44:42.460 --> 00:44:43.020
was unstable.

00:44:43.060 --> 00:44:44.220
What if she hits you?

00:44:44.420 --> 00:44:45.940
She won't do that.

00:44:47.380 --> 00:44:48.580
You stay outside

00:44:48.740 --> 00:44:50.620
and I'll go in.
I'll call you if anything happens

00:44:50.620 --> 00:44:51.380
and you'll come to my rescue.

00:44:51.540 --> 00:44:51.980
Is that okay?

00:44:57.340 --> 00:44:57.900
Alright.

00:44:58.980 --> 00:44:59.860
If anything happens,

00:45:00.060 --> 00:45:00.940
call me.

00:45:01.020 --> 00:45:02.180
Got it. Give it to me.

00:45:03.740 --> 00:45:04.300
Hold it.

00:45:09.300 --> 00:45:10.540
You said you would treat me.

00:45:10.580 --> 00:45:11.620
If you don't come out quickly,

00:45:11.620 --> 00:45:12.700
I'll eat till you're broke.

00:45:30.620 --> 00:45:31.580
Come in.

00:45:40.220 --> 00:45:41.540
Mrs. Zhao, I'm here.

00:45:41.540 --> 00:45:41.860
You're here.

00:45:41.860 --> 00:45:42.340
Yes.

00:45:42.420 --> 00:45:44.180
You brought me fruits again.

00:45:44.460 --> 00:45:44.940
Give it to me.

00:45:46.860 --> 00:45:48.020
They can only be eaten after meals.

00:45:48.540 --> 00:45:49.500
Put your bag here.

00:45:51.700 --> 00:45:52.740
Come and look.

00:45:53.660 --> 00:45:55.300
These are all dishes you like.

00:45:56.340 --> 00:45:57.900
Thank you, Mrs. Zhao. I like them.

00:45:58.100 --> 00:45:58.900
Quickly. Have a seat.

00:45:59.020 --> 00:45:59.300
Okay.

00:45:59.300 --> 00:45:59.700
Mm.

00:46:02.820 --> 00:46:03.380
Sit.

00:46:03.780 --> 00:46:04.620
They must be delicious.

00:46:04.940 --> 00:46:05.620
Here are your chopsticks.

00:46:05.820 --> 00:46:06.340
Thanks.

00:46:06.380 --> 00:46:06.620
Mm.

00:46:07.820 --> 00:46:09.060
The doctor said

00:46:09.060 --> 00:46:10.220
I've almost recovered.

00:46:10.380 --> 00:46:11.860
If I don't get worse,

00:46:12.020 --> 00:46:12.900
I'll be able to leave hospital next week.

00:46:13.060 --> 00:46:13.380
Really?

00:46:13.740 --> 00:46:14.100
Yes.

00:46:14.300 --> 00:46:15.180
Great.

00:46:15.740 --> 00:46:16.860
After I leave hospital,

00:46:17.620 --> 00:46:19.180
can you go to my home?

00:46:19.700 --> 00:46:20.580
Okay.

00:46:20.900 --> 00:46:22.180
I'll make some nice things for you.

00:46:22.180 --> 00:46:22.540
Mm.

00:46:25.620 --> 00:46:26.860
Let me see.

00:46:26.860 --> 00:46:29.460
I'll make Fried Chicken Wings
which Fanzhou likes.

00:46:31.020 --> 00:46:32.220
Actually he can make it, too.

00:46:32.500 --> 00:46:33.540
He makes it better than me.

00:46:34.860 --> 00:46:36.380
He has really learned everything

00:46:36.580 --> 00:46:38.140
to look after me over the years.

00:46:38.540 --> 00:46:38.860
Mm.

00:46:39.180 --> 00:46:41.060
He made it when he came to my house before.

00:46:41.100 --> 00:46:42.060
It was nice.

00:46:43.940 --> 00:46:45.140
He went to your house?

00:46:45.380 --> 00:46:46.140
Mm. Yes.

00:46:47.060 --> 00:46:48.340
I didn't know it at all.

00:46:48.700 --> 00:46:50.260
Perhaps he didn't tell you.

00:46:51.900 --> 00:46:53.020
He is like that sometimes.

00:46:53.580 --> 00:46:54.740
He doesn't tell me anything

00:46:55.620 --> 00:46:57.660
as if he's the only adult in our family,

00:46:58.380 --> 00:46:59.500
just like an old man.

00:47:00.540 --> 00:47:02.260
Sometimes he's really annoying,

00:47:03.220 --> 00:47:03.860
isn't he?

00:47:04.060 --> 00:47:05.380
Yes, he is.

00:47:06.420 --> 00:47:07.140
Oh,

00:47:07.620 --> 00:47:09.540
I secretly asked you to come here.

00:47:09.540 --> 00:47:10.820
You mustn't tell him.

00:47:11.100 --> 00:47:11.940
Otherwise, he'll say,

00:47:11.940 --> 00:47:13.540
"You affected her studies."

00:47:14.500 --> 00:47:15.260
Don't worry, Mrs. Zhao.

00:47:15.260 --> 00:47:16.740
I'm on your side.

00:47:17.540 --> 00:47:19.180
Okay. Let's be on one another's side.

00:47:21.060 --> 00:47:21.900
Eat.

00:47:22.300 --> 00:47:23.300
Have some more, Mrs. Zhao.

00:47:23.300 --> 00:47:23.780
Mm.

00:47:24.220 --> 00:47:24.580
Okay.

00:47:26.300 --> 00:47:27.180
Mrs. Zhao,

00:47:27.620 --> 00:47:29.700
why do you put the food into one box?

00:47:30.460 --> 00:47:32.740
There are many stray dogs
outside the hospital.

00:47:32.820 --> 00:47:34.660
When we take a walk later,

00:47:34.900 --> 00:47:35.500
we can feed them.

00:47:36.180 --> 00:47:36.780
Okay.

00:47:40.220 --> 00:47:41.700
Mom, I'm coming in.

