My mom had a relapse.

00:48:04.140 --> 00:48:05.340
To be honest,

00:48:05.460 --> 00:48:06.620
I've liked her for a long time.

00:48:07.220 --> 00:48:09.180
Is there someone you miss very much?

00:48:09.180 --> 00:48:09.740
Yes.

00:48:09.780 --> 00:48:11.420
Will you miss her greatly

00:48:11.700 --> 00:48:13.980
